#: setup/plugins/blocks/advanced.tpl.php
msgid ""
"The system settings were auto-detected. CiviCRM will be installed with:"
msgstr "Systeminnstillingene ble automatisk oppdaget. CiviCRM vil bli installert med:"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/advanced.tpl.php
msgid "CMS Database"
msgstr "CMS-database"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/advanced.tpl.php
msgid "CiviCRM Database"
msgstr "CiviCRM-database"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/advanced.tpl.php
msgid "Apply"
msgstr "Bruk"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/advanced.tpl.php
msgid ""
"By default, CiviCRM uses the same database as your website. You may install "
"on a separate database if you need more fine-grained control over "
"permissions, replication, hardware capacity, etc."
msgstr "Som standard bruker CiviCRM den samme databasen som nettsiden din. Du kan installere CiviCRM på en separat database hvis du trenger mer finkornet kontroll over tilganger, kopieringer, serverkapasitet, og lignende."

#: setup/plugins/blocks/advanced.tpl.php
msgid "<strong>Example</strong>: <code>%1</code>"
msgstr "<strong>Eksempel</strong>: <code>%1</code>"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/advanced.tpl.php
msgid ""
"Tip: This uses URL notation. If the credentials require any special "
"characters (e.g. \"&\" or \"#\"), then apply URL encoding (e.g. \"%26\" or "
"\"%23\")."
msgstr "Tips: Denne buker URL-notasjon. Hvis nøklene krever noen spesielle tegn (f.eks. \"&\" eller \"#\"), så kan du bruke URL-encoding (f.eks.. \"%26\" eller \"%23\")."

#: setup/plugins/blocks/advanced.tpl.php
msgid "CiviCRM Settings File"
msgstr "CiviCRM Settings-fil"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/advanced.tpl.php
msgid "CiviCRM Source Code"
msgstr "CiviCRM kildekode"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/advanced.tpl.php
msgid ""
"Need more advanced control? You may alternatively use the <a href=\"%1\" "
"target=\"%2\">command-line installer</a>."
msgstr "Trenger du mer avansert kontroll? Du kan alternativt bruke <a href=\"%1\" target=\"%2\">command-line installer</a>."

#: setup/plugins/blocks/components.civi-setup.php
msgid "Accept donations and payments"
msgstr "Motta gaver og betalinger"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/components.civi-setup.php
msgid "Accept event registrations"
msgstr "Motta arrangementsregistreringer"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/components.civi-setup.php
msgid "Send email blasts and newsletters"
msgstr "Send masse-epost utsendelser"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/components.civi-setup.php
msgid "Manage recurring memberships"
msgstr "Administrer gjentagende medlemskap"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/components.civi-setup.php
msgid "Track case histories"
msgstr "Spor sakshistorier"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/components.civi-setup.php
msgid "Accept pledges"
msgstr "Motta lovnader"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/components.civi-setup.php
msgid "Generate reports"
msgstr "Lag rapporter"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/components.civi-setup.php
msgid "Organize campaigns, surveys, and petitions"
msgstr "Organisere kampanjer, undersøkelser og underskriftskampanjer"

#: setup/plugins/blocks/components.tpl.php
msgid "At least one component must be enabled."
msgstr "Minst en komponent må være aktivert."

#: setup/plugins/blocks/components.tpl.php
msgid ""
"Not sure? That's OK. After installing, you can enable and disable components"
" at any time."
msgstr "Ikke sikker? Det er greit. Etter du har installert, kan du aktivere og deaktivere disse komponentene når som helst."

